[
	{
		"id": 0,
		"localized_name": "ハイディの母",
		"romanized_name": "",
		"model_path_hash": "0",
		"text": "……ハイディ、あれからずっと家にいてくれるけど、\nあなたはもう関わらなくてもいいのよ",
		"voice_file": "",
		"still_path_hash": "0",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 1,
		"localized_name": "ハイディの父",
		"romanized_name": "",
		"model_path_hash": "0",
		"text": "ああ。あとは俺たちでなんとかする。\n手を煩わせて悪かった",
		"voice_file": "",
		"still_path_hash": "0",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 2,
		"localized_name": "ハイディ",
		"romanized_name": "Heidi",
		"model_path_hash": "4131218363577277631",
		"text": "なに言ってるの。私も家族なんだよ？\n昔みたいに逃げるのは嫌なんだ",
		"voice_file": "",
		"still_path_hash": "5092952616707211512",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 3,
		"localized_name": "ハイディ",
		"romanized_name": "Heidi",
		"model_path_hash": "4131218363577277631",
		"text": "二人の気持ちも分かるけど、今度はちゃんと\n向き合いたい。どれだけ時間が掛かっても",
		"voice_file": "",
		"still_path_hash": "5092952616707211512",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 4,
		"localized_name": "ハイディの母",
		"romanized_name": "",
		"model_path_hash": "0",
		"text": "……家族って、言ってくれるのね",
		"voice_file": "",
		"still_path_hash": "0",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 5,
		"localized_name": "ハイディ",
		"romanized_name": "Heidi",
		"model_path_hash": "4131218363577277631",
		"text": "二人は心配なんてしてなかったかもしれないけど、\n家出したこと、ずっと引きずってたんだよ",
		"voice_file": "",
		"still_path_hash": "5092952616707211512",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 6,
		"localized_name": "ハイディの母",
		"romanized_name": "",
		"model_path_hash": "0",
		"text": "心配していなかったはずがないでしょう。\n家出してすぐは人を使って探させたりもしたわ",
		"voice_file": "",
		"still_path_hash": "0",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 7,
		"localized_name": "ハイディの母",
		"romanized_name": "",
		"model_path_hash": "0",
		"text": "教会に身を寄せたと知ってからは、\n無理に干渉しないようにしたけれど……",
		"voice_file": "",
		"still_path_hash": "0",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 8,
		"localized_name": "ハイディの父",
		"romanized_name": "",
		"model_path_hash": "0",
		"text": "俺たち夫婦が家出の原因なのは明らかだったし、\n申し訳なくて……",
		"voice_file": "",
		"still_path_hash": "0",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 9,
		"localized_name": "ハイディの母",
		"romanized_name": "",
		"model_path_hash": "0",
		"text": "でも、カロリンさんを通じて、あなたが自立して\n元気にやっていると聞いて、安心していたのよ",
		"voice_file": "",
		"still_path_hash": "0",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 10,
		"localized_name": "ハイディ",
		"romanized_name": "Heidi",
		"model_path_hash": "4131218363577277631",
		"text": "……なるほど。カロリンとはその時からの\n縁だったってことか",
		"voice_file": "",
		"still_path_hash": "5092952616707211512",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 11,
		"localized_name": "ハイディ",
		"romanized_name": "Heidi",
		"model_path_hash": "0",
		"text": "（心配してただなんて、昔の私だったら\n　絶対に信じられなかっただろう）",
		"voice_file": "",
		"still_path_hash": "5092952616707211512",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 12,
		"localized_name": "ハイディ",
		"romanized_name": "Heidi",
		"model_path_hash": "0",
		"text": "（でも、今の私なら分かる。\n　それが本心だって）",
		"voice_file": "",
		"still_path_hash": "5092952616707211512",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 13,
		"localized_name": "ハイディ",
		"romanized_name": "Heidi",
		"model_path_hash": "0",
		"text": "（私に用意してくれてた新しい服……\n　今の私にぴったりだった）",
		"voice_file": "",
		"still_path_hash": "5092952616707211512",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 14,
		"localized_name": "ハイディ",
		"romanized_name": "Heidi",
		"model_path_hash": "0",
		"text": "（きっと、毎年。私が帰ってくることを願って、\n　用意してたんだ）",
		"voice_file": "",
		"still_path_hash": "5092952616707211512",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 15,
		"localized_name": "ハイディ",
		"romanized_name": "Heidi",
		"model_path_hash": "4131218363577277631",
		"text": "……ねえ、母さん。家族ってさ、\nかけがえのないものなんだ",
		"voice_file": "",
		"still_path_hash": "5092952616707211512",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 16,
		"localized_name": "ハイディ",
		"romanized_name": "Heidi",
		"model_path_hash": "4131218363577277631",
		"text": "世の中には、もっとひどい親もいるし……\n親すらいない人だっている",
		"voice_file": "",
		"still_path_hash": "5092952616707211512",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 17,
		"localized_name": "ハイディ",
		"romanized_name": "Heidi",
		"model_path_hash": "4131218363577277631",
		"text": "そんな中で、ちゃんと血の繋がった親がいて、\nこうしてまだ話すことができるのは幸せなことなんだよ",
		"voice_file": "",
		"still_path_hash": "5092952616707211512",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 18,
		"localized_name": "ハイディ",
		"romanized_name": "Heidi",
		"model_path_hash": "4131218363577277631",
		"text": "そんな家族をバラバラになんて、したくないんだ。\n家出した私が言うなって話かもしれないけど……",
		"voice_file": "",
		"still_path_hash": "5092952616707211512",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 19,
		"localized_name": "ハイディ",
		"romanized_name": "Heidi",
		"model_path_hash": "4131218363577277631",
		"text": "娘のわがままだって思って、父さんのこともう一度考え\n直してくれないかな。その上で無理なら仕方ないけどさ",
		"voice_file": "",
		"still_path_hash": "5092952616707211512",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 20,
		"localized_name": "ハイディの母",
		"romanized_name": "",
		"model_path_hash": "0",
		"text": "……そうね。あれから毎日、謝られ続けて、\nもう怒りも失せてきたわ。考えてみる",
		"voice_file": "",
		"still_path_hash": "0",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 21,
		"localized_name": "ハイディ",
		"romanized_name": "Heidi",
		"model_path_hash": "4131218363577277631",
		"text": "……いいの？",
		"voice_file": "",
		"still_path_hash": "5092952616707211512",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 22,
		"localized_name": "ハイディの母",
		"romanized_name": "",
		"model_path_hash": "0",
		"text": "もちろん、不正のことは、絶対に許さないわ。\n取り返すくらいに必死に働いてもらうから",
		"voice_file": "",
		"still_path_hash": "0",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 23,
		"localized_name": "ハイディの父",
		"romanized_name": "",
		"model_path_hash": "0",
		"text": "はい！　喜んで働きます！　\nなんでもします！",
		"voice_file": "",
		"still_path_hash": "0",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 24,
		"localized_name": "ハイディ",
		"romanized_name": "Heidi",
		"model_path_hash": "4131218363577277631",
		"text": "いやーこんな綺麗にまとまりそうとは、よかったぁ",
		"voice_file": "",
		"still_path_hash": "5092952616707211512",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 25,
		"localized_name": "ハイディの母",
		"romanized_name": "",
		"model_path_hash": "0",
		"text": "昔からこういうところがある人だっていうのは\n分かってたもの。私がいないとダメみたい",
		"voice_file": "",
		"still_path_hash": "0",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 26,
		"localized_name": "ハイディの母",
		"romanized_name": "",
		"model_path_hash": "0",
		"text": "相手を受け入れて許す気概がなければ、\n結婚なんてできないものよ",
		"voice_file": "",
		"still_path_hash": "0",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 27,
		"localized_name": "カロリン",
		"romanized_name": "Caroline",
		"model_path_hash": "5485149628928083359",
		"text": "それもまた、愛の形ですね",
		"voice_file": "",
		"still_path_hash": "5434631736340677129",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 28,
		"localized_name": "ハイディ",
		"romanized_name": "Heidi",
		"model_path_hash": "4131218363577277631",
		"text": "なるほど",
		"voice_file": "",
		"still_path_hash": "5092952616707211512",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	}
]